# ChangeLog

## v1.0.0

Fixed some bug
New features:
- add new page: mermaid, asciibox support preview and save as svg
- reImp settings, it will not depend on gtk settings, using ~/.config/asciibox/asciibox.toml instead
- reImp resource, it will not depend on asciibox.resource in $pkg_dir, resource is self-contained now
- reImp ui, it's using left dock to navigate and using sourceview to edit

## v0.9.1

Fixed table format bug
New features:

- support gfm markdown style table format

## v0.9.0

Fixed table format bug
New features:

- support input markdown/asciibox table format
- support table format which copy from web

## v0.8.4

Fixed some render bug
New features:

- support up/down arrow in svgbob generate
- support multiple left/right arrow in svgbob generate


## v0.8.3

Remove nom dependency
Fixed some render bug

## v0.8.2

Finally the first version has been released!!!
And while it's still pretty weak, it's ready to be used on a basic level

New features:

- support basic svgbob generate
- support beautify asciidoc table
